# Registration


## Create user


### Resource

`<%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/auth`


### URL parameters

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### Query String

Parameter | Description | Required
--------- | ----------- | --------


### HTTP request method

`POST`


### HTTP headers

Key | Value
--------- | -----------
Content-Type | multipart/form-data


### HTTP body

Mandatory form fields:

 * `first_name`;
 * `last_name`;
 * `username`;
 * `email`;
 * `password`;
 * `confirm_success_url`.


### Note

> HTTP example request

```http
POST <%= ENV['APP_HOSTNAME'] %>/auth
```

```http
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
```

```shell
  first_name = first
  last_name = last
  username = username1
  email = username1@example.com
  password = hh41yW6J62CuaFeANuDYcOWkH
  confirm_success_url = https://example.com
```


> HTTP response 200 OK
